What a special lady.

35
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,200
Alright.

36
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,000
I will grant you three wishes.

37
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,560
Tell me.

38
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,240
Here's the first wish.

39
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:56,200
The constables of the Daoming Court
solved the case

40
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,200
and should be exempt from penalties.

41
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:00,680
Granted.

42
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,200
Everyone, please rise.

43
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,720
Here's the second wish.

44
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,360
Please issue a decree

45
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,240
to forbid all high officials

46
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:11,120
