47
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,440
and ladies of low status

48
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,960
and peculiar occupations.

49
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,800
Protect the rights of women.

50
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:18,120
Abolish all laws
that are detrimental to women.

51
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,880
