57
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:34,960
is a pure torment.

58
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:36,880
Granted.

59
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:41,000
You truly are different.

60
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:43,040
The first two wishes

61
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,800
were made for the sake of others.

62
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,040
I bet you're keeping

63
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:49,360
the third wish for yourself, right?

64
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:50,840
That's right.

65
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,480
It is for myself.

66
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,160
Please make me

67
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,960
the leader of the Daoming Court,

68
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,880
so that I can
arrest Yun Zhishui in person.

69
