71
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,840
That will help me bring him back

72
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,760
as soon as possible.

73
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,320
Lin Lusheng, heed the command.

74
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,880
I hereby order you
to arrest the criminal Yun Zhishui.

75
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,480
Make sure he's alive

76
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,880
for my interrogation.

77
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,840
You gentlemen here assisted

78
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,320
in solving the case.

79
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:34,120
I grant you 10,000 taels
of gold and silver

80
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,760
