113
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,080
Are you really

114
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,240
going to arrest Zhishui?

115
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,560
Yeah, I want to arrest him in person.

116
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:26,840
This is to protect him.

117
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,440
He'd be in danger

118
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,240
