119
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,400
Thank you

120
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,240
for thinking about the four of us.

121
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,120
I came here because of

122
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,240
the four of you.

123
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,520
Can't it be just because of me?

124
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,320
Right now,

125
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:56,040
I'm here only for you.

126
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,640
Let's eat.

127
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,880
Let's eat.

128
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,440
What did you write?

129
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,600
Not telling you.

130
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,840
It won't work if I do.

131
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,600
Come on.

132
00:06:21,728 --> 00:06:22,320
Come on.

133
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,280
One, two, three.

134
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,040
Thank you.

135
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,680
What for?

136
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,120
Thank you

137
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,320
