138
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,120
What do you mean?

139
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,160
Don't make me hit you.

140
00:07:09,523 --> 00:07:12,640
♪Carrying the one who's leaving♪

141
00:07:13,888 --> 00:07:17,280
♪The mountain casts a shadow♪

142
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:20,320
On the day I met you,

143
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,400
I...

144
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:23,920
I felt

145
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,160
that my life began to change.

146
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,080
I used to

147
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,760
think about nothing but revenge.

148
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,480
But you know what?

149
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,480
I saw kindness

150
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,040
and compassion

151
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,320
