160
00:08:13,088 --> 00:08:19,584
♪All poured into the river of yearning♪

161
00:08:35,731 --> 00:08:41,040
(Pan Jinlian's Fragrance Shop)

162
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:41,880
Little Deer.

163
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,040
What are you doing here?

164
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,760
Young Master Han.

165
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:45,800
What's up?

166
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,960
May you be well, leader.

167
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,240
Enough.

168
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:50,840
Here.

169
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,760
The new flavor of Lianxiang House.

170
00:08:53,024 --> 00:08:53,560
Thank you.

171
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,480
What are you up to?

172
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,200
Where is Wumian?

173
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,320
Oh.

174
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,000
Hedgehog

175
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,560
