has resurfaced.

179
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,320
So I'm looking for Wumian.

180
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,400
Did Commander Han send you?

181
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:06,960
No.

182
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,520
He's still resting in bed.

183
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:11,440
He's never recovered from the stab

184
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,320
at the Pinxiang Meeting.

185
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:13,920
Besides,

186
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:15,880
