187
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,000
You are the leader.

188
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:18,400
Most importantly,

189
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:20,040
I want to prove myself

190
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,120
