191
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,800
Let's find Hedgehog first.

192
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:26,480
My goodness.

193
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:29,400
I didn't expect Zhishui
to be hiding in such a place.

194
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,240
We've been investigating for a long time

195
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:33,520
and found some traces nearby.

196
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:34,920
I suspect

197
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:36,080
