198
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,000
Little Deer.

199
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,680
What should we do

200
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:40,440
if we find him?

201
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,200
Arrest him?

202
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:46,800
Let's first ask him
about the assassination

203
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:47,720
and Mo Shanghua.

204
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,320
Yeah.

205
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:49,480
Oh, right.

206
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:50,520
Any news

207
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,560
while we were away from

208
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,640
the Daoming Court?

209
00:09:58,560 --> 00:09:59,360
Little Deer.

210
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,360
