216
00:10:16,243 --> 00:10:21,631
♪Who is admiring
their own solitary elegance♪

217
00:10:21,631 --> 00:10:27,359
♪Strolling leisurely in the courtyard♪

218
00:10:27,359 --> 00:10:32,447
♪Dust adheres to the brick walls♪

219
00:10:32,447 --> 00:10:39,007
♪So stubborn, can't bear to collide♪

220
00:10:39,007 --> 00:10:44,703
♪Who weaves garments
of feathers and rainbow silks♪

221
00:10:44,703 --> 00:10:50,591
♪Contented with oneself
amidst the chaotic world♪

222
00:10:50,591 --> 00:10:55,743
♪Who lets the lonely petals fall♪

223
00:10:55,743 --> 00:11:03,647
♪Scattering in the city
filled with flying ash♪

224
00:11:03,647 --> 00:11:08,639
